titleInfo.title: 'WEST INDIA ISLANDS AND CARIBBEAN SEA. SHEET I. COMPRISING FLORIDA STRAIT, BAHAMA ISLANDS AND GREATER ANTILLES. Compiled from most recent surveys. 1876. With corrections to 1937.'

physicalDescription.extent: Materials: printed on paper.Dimensions: 660 x 990mm, on sheet 710 x 1040mm.

mods.abstract: Published at the Admiralty, London, 3 July 1876. New editions and corrections listed to 1947.Soundings listed in fathoms.Settlements, roads, hydrology, and relief indicated.Letter from the Admiralty to the Colonial Office dated 24 March 1947 (folio 119) relates to this map.
